data.meta_description: 4 likes, 0 comments - alamocville on March 6, 2024: "A commitment-phobic bachelor is tempted to change his ways after meeting the woman of his dreams in FOUR WEDDINGS AND A FUNERAL, starring Hugh Grant, Andie MacDowell and Kristin Scott Thomas.
